snippet.textDisplay: I envision a possilbe future where XFL teams are promoted or relegated to the NFL. Instead of having the two league franchises merge, as one might expect, they instead compete in a greater system that culminates in an event where the NFL Super Bowl Champions play against the XFL Super Bowl Champions for the true title of "World Champions of Football". As is, the differing rule sets between the leagues are a barrier to this vision.
